\begin_layout Subsection
Speech Detection
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The first part of the project aims at implementing a speech recognition and distinguish the different colors. Therefore the module "ALSpeechRecognition" was used. It provides the event listener "WordRecognized". When subscribed to this module, an event is thrown when a word is recognized from the vocabulary list which is specified beforehand. Once the event is detected and thrown, the program jumps to the method "OnColorHeard", there a simple if-query determines the color. Afterwards the next method is called which is described in the following section. 
\end_layout

